Follow instructions on packaging & enjoy!

> Don't have a go-to fishmonger? No problem! Our friends at GoodChop deliver high-quality, hormone and antibiotic-free meat and seafood right to your door. Add this special box packed with our four favorites from under the sea to your HelloFresh order to fortify your weekly meals, or just to have on hand. In this box, you'll receive Alaskan sockeye salmon (30 ounces), Alaskan halibut (8 ounces), Gulf shrimp (1 pound), and Pacific cod (30 ounces). The best part? All of GoodChop's seafood products are wild-caught off the coasts of the USA!

> Your order will ship separately in a Good Chop-branded box and may not arrive on your scheduled weekly HF delivery date (shipping is included in the total price). Customization of bundles is not available at this time.

@Wild-Caught Alaskan Sockeye Salmon{30%ounces}
@Alaskan Halibut{8%ounces}
@Gulf Shrimp{1%pound}
@Wild-Caught Pacific Cod{30%ounces}

